*Stingtra smiled at the way Quickstrike was proud of himself* Stingtra: I'll
clean up. *Stingtra begins picking up the pan and then she falls asleep and
wakes up. She was terribley tired from the nights of watching over
Quickstrike but her spark told her to it not only because he was second in
command. She even did it when he didn't tell her too* Stingtra: Just...gonna
clean up. *Stingtra punched herself and chuckled* *Stingtra was now wide
awake* Stingtra: Anything else? *Stingtra said to Quickstrike*

he

>
> He wasn't going to have it. The instant the red dactyl came in arms

> Quickstrike threw his arm out and stuck his head. Terrorsaur's long beak

>
> "Beat ya to it!" the young Fuzor snapped at the dactyl, mocking him. "Go
get
> yer own!" He laughed in a victorious way. "Did ya see that?" he said to
> Stingtra. He was just too proud of himself.
>
> He transformed to his beast mode and snatched the meat up. He crawled away
> from Stingtra and went to a place where he could eat.
